      "title": "Unique Mechanic: Weapon Draw",
      "text": [
        "Excalibur. Double damage!\nExcalibur. Double damage!\nExcalipoor. 1 damage...\nExcalipoor. 1 damage...",
        "Gilgamesh draws one of eight weapons with a melee attack. Each weapon has unique traits, such as weapon length, EX gauge depletion or different base damage |",
        "The attack's baseline damage value before equipment and stats are considered.",
        ". All weapons are drawn at random with a set probability. Weapon is not drawn when using Wind Slash, Electrocute, Rocket Punch or Missile.",
        "The weapons' base damage affects the attack's base damage, not the final damage. This is one of the few mechanics that affect an attack's base damage, which means everything scales with builds (higher ATK etc.)."
      ],
