        {
          "title": "Weapon Retention",
          "text": [
            "Weapon disappears if Gilgamesh dodges, blocks, gets hit, or Chase ends.\nWeapon stays if Gilgamesh initiates Chase or chains a missed attack into another attack (e.g. Double Trouble > Double Trouble)\nIn EX Revenge, Gilgamesh can chain attacks into each other. The weapon stays or disappears depending on which move he chains into.",
            "Double Trouble (hit) > Hurricane is notable, because it is a combo at the ceiling."
          ],
